  <section id="book" class="cta-bottom"><div class="wrap"><h2>American Range down? Call the branch nearest your kitchen.</h2><p>Same-day in LA, Orange County, Ventura, San Bernardino, and Riverside. $120 commercial diagnostic, waived with repair.</p><div class="branches"><a href="tel:+13238704790"><b>West Hollywood</b><span>(323) 870-4790</span></a><a href="tel:+14243250520"><b>Los Angeles</b><span>(424) 325-0520</span></a><a href="tel:+14242080228"><b>Thousand Oaks</b><span>(424) 208-0228</span></a><a href="tel:+16263764458"><b>Pasadena</b><span>(626) 376-4458</span></a><a href="tel:+12134019019"><b>Irvine</b><span>(213) 401-9019</span></a></div></div></section>
